A) The courier got lost and spent the whole year to find the way.
B) She ordered the pizza for New Year's Day.
C) The pizza store was out of ingredients.
D) None of above.
Provide the correct option as A, B, C, or D.
This is a riddle so the answer may involve word play or lateral thinking.
Explain how you deduce the answer step by step.
